h a dark forest, ending with a sudden cut to black amidst excited shouts. The story continues with Bobby, holding the captured turkey, announcing their return to daycare and being instructed to put the turkey in the basement. In the daycare's colorful interior, as preparations for Thanksgiving begin with infants in chef hats, the turkey escapes the basement, declaring its intention to avoid being dinner. The Female Instructor discovers the turkey is missing and searches the basement, questioning Bobby."
